-- Ferrovial to Complete Sale of 10% Stake in Toronto 407 Highway This Year
-- Sharon Smyth
-- 2010-06-29T12:09:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/ferrovial-to-complete-sale-of-10-stake-in-toronto-407-highway-this-year.html

          
          
             Ferrovial SA expects to receive
binding offers for a 10 percent stake in its 407 Express
Toll Route highway in Toronto in July and to complete the sale
this year, Chief Executive Officer Inigo Meiras said today in
Madrid.   
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        